      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">The Maestro Problem: Chamath Is Right About the Job. He Is Wrong About the Hard Part.</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Chamath Palihapitiya and David Sacks just described the most important emerging role in AI: the "maestro of agents." They are right about the role. They are missing the hard part. The challenge is not building agents. It is getting them to work as a team.</p>
